20","price":798.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/best_multivitamin_for_men.webp?v=1770728293"},{"product_id":"hair-skin-vitamins-capsules-glowing-healthy","title":"Neuherbs Hair Vitamins Tablets","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eDaily exposure to pollution, stress, and an unhealthy diet can weaken hair from the roots, leading to dull, dry, thin hair with easy breakage. The good news? These are modifiable factors—and with the right nutrition, you can restore your hair strength and vitality. neuherbs Hair Vitamins Tablets for Hair Nourishment offer a complete solution for stronger, healthier, and more voluminous hair. This one-a-day hair vitamin formula combines 3 Clinically-Backed Blends including daily nourishment blend combining 15 essential vitamins and minerals—Biotin, natural Vitamin C, Zinc, and Iron—to bridge nutritional gaps, reduce oxidative stress, and repair hair follicles from within. Powered by the amino acids—featuring L-Lysine, L-Cysteine, L-Methionine (crucial for hair structure) and time-tested herbs like Amla, Rosemary, and Hibiscus extracts—they support keratin synthesis to strengthen hair strands, reduce hair greying, and promote thicker hair. Unlike typical hair supplements that focus only on hair fall, these biotin tablets provide comprehensive nourishment, repair, and strength, delivering 100% RDA of Biotin for visible volume and shine. To ensure maximum efficacy, neuherbs hair vitamin tablets include piperine from black pepper, which enhances nutrient absorption and bioavailability. Whether you're dealing with hair thinning, breakage, or simply wanting to boost your hair health, these tablets support your journey to healthier hair from the inside out.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (60 Capsules)","offer_id":40975837167786,"sku":"NHSNC60","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"2 Months Pack - (120 Capsules)=Recommended","offer_id":41395594166442,"sku":"NHSNC60P2-1","price":1328.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/hair_vitamin_supplements_1.webp?v=1767444365"},{"product_id":"milk-thistle-capsules-liver-skin-health","title":"High Strength Milk Thistle Capsules For Liver Health","description":"\u003cp\u003eRegular alcohol consumption, smoking, antibiotics, painkillers, and junk food can often harm the liver by accumulating toxins. Milk Thistle is a flowering herb belonging to the daisy family. In traditional Ayurvedic practices, milk thistle can be used for problems related to the liver, owing to an active ingredient called Silymarin, which is an essential antioxidant that may have protective effects on the liver. neuherbs Milk Thistle capsules contain 800 mg of Silymarin and can help maintain liver health, reduce body inflammation, and improve overall health naturally.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (60 Capsules)","offer_id":40975847620778,"sku":"NMT60","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"2 Months Pack - (120 Capsules)=Recommended","offer_id":44266746740906,"sku":"NMT60P2","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/bestmilkthistlesupplement.jpg?v=1713168571"},{"product_id":"ashwagandha-1000-plus-tablets-stress-relief","title":"Ashwagandha 1000 Plus Tablets – Daily Lifestyle Support","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs Ashwagandha 1000 Plus is made with natural ashwagandha root extract, Vitamin E, and B-complex (B6, B9, B12), along with piperine. This blend is designed to \u003cstrong data-start=\"1412\" data-end=\"1497\"\u003ehelp maintain balance, support an active lifestyle, and promote everyday wellness\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"