price":889.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard3148.jpg?v=1735025127"},{"product_id":"vitamin-e-plus-capsules-skin-hair","title":"Vitamin E Plus Capsules – Skin \u0026 Hair Wellness Support","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVitamin E is a fat-soluble vitamin and a natural source of antioxidants that support overall wellness. neuherbs Vitamin E Plus capsules are plant-based and sourced from sunflower oil, enriched with almond oil and MCT oil (medium chain triglycerides) for optimal absorption.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e This formula is designed to support healthy skin and hair as part of a balanced wellness routine. It provides a combination of natural vitamin E and supportive nutrients to help maintain skin hydration, promote antioxidant protection, and contribute to overall hair and skin wellness. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eneuherbs Vitamin E Plus is a 3-in-1 supportive formula for skin and hair health, designed for everyday wellness.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (30 Capsules)","offer_id":41893293031594,"sku":"NVEP30","price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"2 Month Pack - (60 Capsules)","offer_id":47967643893930,"sku":"NVEP60","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Vitamin_e_plus_1.jpg?v=1770722211"},{"product_id":"cotton-tshirt","title":"neuherbs White Cotton T-shirt","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs White Cotton T-shirt is something easy to throw on whenever you need a quick and stylish layer. This crew neck t-shirt has a plain, adaptable design and hides a whole host of benefits. The pure cotton T-shirt has a simple style and is luxuriously soft. It has the classic-looking logo of neuherbs on it that enhances its beauty magnificently. Wearing this T-shirt can simply make you feel fabulous and fresh.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul class=\"tabs\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eIs it mixed cotton?\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNo this neuherbs T-Shirt is made up of 100% Cotton.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eIs black colour available in this t-shirt?\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNo this neuherbs 100% cotton t-shirt is available in white colour only with a very light weight \u0026amp; high quality.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eIs it only avilable in medium size?\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNo, neuherbs cotton t-shirt is also avilable in two different sizes large \u0026amp; extra large.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eIs it returnable?\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYes, it is returnable \u0026amp; exchangable as well.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eIs it machine washable?\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYes, it is machine washable.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eIs it made in India? \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYes. this neuherbs light weighted 100% cotton t-shirt is a Made in India product. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"M","offer_id":42487983734954,"sku":"NWCTM","price":499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":42487983767722,"sku":"61099090","price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":42487983800490,"sku":"NWCTXL","price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/products\/NeuherbsWhiteCottonT-shirt.jpg?v=1646468473"},{"product_id":"anti-aging-combo-skin-collagen-vitamin-e-plus","title":"Anti-Aging Combo: Skin Collagen + Vitamin E Plus for Better Face \u0026 Hair","description":"\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\" class=\"sort-description\"\u003eSkin collagen is the most commonly found protein in our body that is known to manage skin texture, skin elasticity, and skin health. If you wish to have young and wrinkle-free skin forever, you must source collagen externally from best collagen supplements and consume it regularly. neuherbs offers the best collagen supplement for the skin as it supports our body’s collagen production and helps reduce the signs of aging. neuherbs Collagen booster powder is loaded with hyaluronic acid and biotin. neuherbs collagen supplement for skin contains Vitamin C that promotes collagen production.  Vitamin E, on the other hand, also has multiple benefits for improving hair and skin quality. Vitamin E helps moisturize the skin and promotes wound healing. Vitamin E may also decrease dryness, skin itching, and flaking, and may also manage eczema symptoms, making it one of the most beneficial vitamins for skin and hair. Which is why we bring to you neuherbs plant-based vitamin E oil capsules alongside our Skin collagen booster, to provide several essential benefits to your skin and hair, helping reduce skin inflammation, skin texture and manage early signs of aging. All while providing the very needed moisture to your dry and dull skin. So, choose our unique combo, made just for you and get a glow and confidence, like never before .\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (200GM + 30 N Capsules)","offer_id":43368235860138,"sku":"NVMSC6","price":1398.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Veg_collagen_with_Vitamin_E.jpg?v=1763977061"},{"product_id":"pure-himalayan-shilajit-resin-boost-stamina","title":"Pure Himalayan Shilajit Resin - Boost Stamina \u0026 Strength","description":"\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\" class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShilajit is a traditional Ayurvedic herb that has been used for centuries to help people with low stamina, endurance, and vitality. neuherbs shilajit resin is sourced from the high altitudes of the Himalayas for high potency \u0026amp; better results. neuherbs Pure Himalayan Shilajit Resin is purified using a Traditional Ayurvedic technique known as Suryataapi to retain its nutrients, benefits, and effectiveness. So, try neuherbs ’ Pure Himalayan Shilajit Resin and improve your strength, stamina \u0026amp; energy while reducing fatigue and getting your testosterone levels significantly higher. Since it is sourced from high ~18000 ft. altitudes, it offers you up to 75% of fulvic acid and the most potent form for optimal absorption and efficacy. neuherbs Pure Himalayan Shilajit is completely safe as it is tested for heavy metals from NABL.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Shilajit - (20 GM)","offer_id":44586359816362,"sku":"NPHS20","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Shilajit - (30 GM)=Recommended","offer_id":44363347951786,"sku":"NPHS30","price":999.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Pure_himalayan_shilajit_resin_1.webp?v=1769506439"},{"product_id":"green-coffee-instant-charge-weight-loss","title":"Green Coffee Instant Charge Tablets for Energy Boost","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eGreen Coffee Instant Charge effervescent tablets allow both men and women to enjoy several great health benefits — from charging up your body to boosting your metabolism \u0026amp; workout performance. neuherbs  Green Coffee has several beneficial implications for your diet due to its pure, antioxidant rich nature. The effervescent formula, made from scientifically studied ingredients like green coffee extracts, Vitamin B, \u0026amp; natural caffeine offers a refreshing boost of energy and has been scientifically proven to improve metabolism. Also adding the perk of Vitamin B6 and B12 in your body, neuherbs  Green Coffee effervescent tablets offer you effective energy with zero added sugar or added calories.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Starter Pack - (20 Tablets)","offer_id":44663805018282,"sku":"NGCICCCF20ET","price":299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Smart Pack -  (60 Tablets)","offer_id":43302958661802,"sku":"NGCICCCF20ETP3","price":897.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Value Pack - (120 Tablets)=Recommended","offer_id":43302958694570,"sku":"NGCICCCF20ETP6","price":1099.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard_5_copy_6.jpg?v=1734005697"},{"product_id":"apple-cider-vinegar-effervescent-tablets","title":"Effervescent Apple Cider Vinegar Tablets","description":"\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\" class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEnjoy the benefits of Apple Cider Vinegar in a convenient form with neuherbs Apple Cider Vinegar Effervescent Tablets! Add these plant-based tablets to your diet to support cholesterol management, weight loss, metabolism boost, appetite control, and gut health. Made from Himalayan apples, they also offer antioxidant support from pomegranate extract to combat oxidative stress and promote overall well-being. With added Vitamin B6 and B12, they help boost energy metabolism to keep you energized. Carry them wherever you go and enjoy their delicious, fizzy taste anytime.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Apple Flavour - (20 Tablets)","offer_id":44760418320554,"sku":"NACVAF20ET","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Smart Pack - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":43302962036906,"sku":"NACVAF20ETP3","price":499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Watermelon Flavour - (20 Tablets)","offer_id":46223803383978,"sku":"NACVWF20ET","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Orange Flavour - (20 Tablets)","offer_id":46223803515050,"sku":"NACVOF20ET","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/apple_cider_vineger_tablets_1.png?v=1752643821"},{"product_id":"organic-ashwagandha-powder-energy-stress-relief","title":"Ashwagandha Powder - Boost Energy, Reduce Stress","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eAshwagandha is an evergreen Ayurvedic medicinal herb that’s been used for over 3000 years to promote health and wellbeing. Also referred to as the Indian Ginseng, Ashwagandha helps rejuvenate body and mind alike, manage stress, improve mood, induce calmness, increase stamina and energy levels, manage inflammation, and reduce oxidative stress. Ashwagandha helps manage insomnia, stress, anxiety, and promote calmness in mind \u0026amp; body. Ashwagandha also contains antioxidants that are known to improve immunity. Ashwagandha powders are designed to improve sleep quality and sleep cycle, relax the mind, and manage tiredness and general fatigue that’s associated with all day stress. neuherbs 100% pure \u0026amp; natural Ashwagandha Powder is made from the finest Ashwagandha root to access the maximum benefits of withanolides:the active ingredient of ashwagandha. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Pack of 1  - (100 GM)","offer_id":43426208776362,"sku":"NOASP100","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Pack of 2 - (100+100)GM","offer_id":45801787293866,"sku":"NOASP100P2","price":398.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Ashwagandha_powder_1_668accd6-0b57-4208-9f34-d349d5e07884.png?v=1766468142"},{"product_id":"organic-safed-musli-powder","title":"Organic Safed Musli Powder for men's support of vitality, reduced physical weakness and high performance.","description":"\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDerived from the roots of the Chlorophytum borivilianum plant, neuherbs brings to you its safed musli powder — a supplement known for its benefits for vitality \u0026amp; performance. Safed Musli Powder benefits you by enhancing the vitality of your body, while also helping with energy \u0026amp; body strength. This magical Ayurvedic herb acts as a natural performance booster that helps reduce physical weakness \u0026amp; boost performance. neuherbs Organic Safed Musli Powder for male does not contain added preservatives, artificial colour or flavour to give you authentic Safed Musli powder benefits, making it the best supplement for male wellness.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Pack of 1  - (100 GM)","offer_id":43426019672234,"sku":"NOSMP100","price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Pack of 2 - (100+100)GM","offer_id":45801853845674,"sku":"NOSMP100P2","price":798.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Organic_safed_musli_powder_1.webp?v=1762412502"},{"product_id":"organic-mulethi-powder-skin-throat","title":"Mulethi Powder for Skin Tightening \u0026 Sore Throat","description":"\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMulethi is a popular and traditional Ayurvedic herb and is high in antioxidants, antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties. The active ingredient in Mulethi, is glycyrrhizin which imparts a mild sweet taste to mulethi. Mulethi Root Powder is also a great source of proteins, amino acids, polysaccharides, minerals \u0026amp; vitamins. Mulethi root powder is known for its beneficial effects on skin \u0026amp; respiratory health. Its anti-inflammatory properties help reduce skin inflammation resulting in brighter, clearer, and healthier skin. So, improve your skin health and well-being with neuherbs pure Mulethi Powder made from Mulethi root or licorice in a clean and certified facility. neuherbs Mulethi root powder does not contain artificial flavours, colours, or preservatives, ensuring a high-quality product with highly active nutrients. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Pack of 1  - (100 GM)","offer_id":43426081669290,"sku":"NOMLP100","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Pack of 2 - (100+100)GM","offer_id":45801945170090,"sku":"NOMLP100P2","price":398.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/mulethi_powder_1_4282b39f-9366-48d2-878e-bfaa79e92635.webp?v=1771589575"},{"product_id":"organic-amla-powder-hair-skin-health","title":"Amla Powder: Boost Hair \u0026 Skin Health","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eAmla, or Indian Gooseberry powder, offers multiple health benefits for hair, skin, and gut health. It is loaded with nutrients and is the richest source of Vitamin C. Therefore, it is widely used in Ayurveda to boost immunity, fight oxidative stress, and reduce inflammation in the body. Amla is also known to improve stamina and defend the body against free-radical damage. Amla is sweet and sour and contains astringent properties, making it a superfood in Ayurveda. Amla Powder can be made into a nourishing tonic\/drink to help brighten skin, purify circulation, strengthen gut health, and improve hair. Amla Powder by neuherbs can help improve skin elasticity from within, manage dull \u0026amp; dry skin \u0026amp; scalp, \u0026amp; support a healthy digestion. Amla is effective in managing early signs of aging by boosting collagen production and fighting scalp tissue damage due to UV rays.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Pack of 1 - (100 GM)","offer_id":43426103328938,"sku":"NOAMP100","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Pack of 2  - (100+100)GM","offer_id":45801908994218,"sku":"NOAMP100P2","price":398.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Amla_powder_1.webp?v=1760078423"},{"product_id":"organic-shatavari-powder-womens-health","title":"Organic Shatavari Powder For Women's Hormonal Balance","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eShatavari root is an Ayurvedic medicinal herb used extensively in Ayurveda to promote women’s reproductive health and wellness. neuherbs  organic Shatavari Powder is a crucial herbal tonic that helps improve women's hormones and strength by nourishing, strengthening, and maintaining the female reproductive health. neuherbs  Shatavari powder is prepared using organic Shatavari roots in a quality-controlled and certified facility. Our highly efficient Shatavari Powder offers various health benefits—it helps improve digestion, regulate the female reproductive system, reduce body fatigue and boost physical strength. It may also help you manage hormonal imbalance. As an ayurvedic herb, Shatavari also helps our body to cope with stress, anxiety, and mood swings.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Pack of 1 - (100 GM)","offer_id":43426126725290,"sku":"NOSTP100","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Pack of 2 - (100+100)GM","offer_id":45801897099434,"sku":"NOSTP100P2","price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Shatavari_powder_1.webp?v=1762412855"},{"product_id":"organic-moringa-powder-immunity-weight-loss","title":"Moringa Powder for Immunity, Weight Loss, Gut Health","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eMoringa are the leaves of a delicious vegetable drumstick. Also known as the miracle tree or ben oil tree, moringa is highly nutritious and loaded with antioxidants and anti-inflammatory properties. It is also rich in Vitamin A, C, and B complex, Calcium, Iron, Magnesium, and Dietary Fiber. Moringa leaves are low in fat and don’t contain bad cholesterol. Moringa leaf has a unique and delicious taste – popularly used in dals, sabjis, chapati dough, and smoothies etc. Moringa leaves offer a wealth of health benefits, ranging from enhancing immunity, supporting weight loss, promoting a healthy gut, to improving vision. Buy Moringa Leaf Powder, which is 100% preservative and additive-free, pure, and natural by neuherbs. The neuherbs moringa powder is also an excellent source of Amino acids and, therefore, is known to increase stamina, vitality, and energy levels. Consuming neuherbs Moringa Powder regularly can ensure better health and well-being, so grab now.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Starter Pack - (100 GM)","offer_id":43426143338666,"sku":"NOMRP100","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Saver Pack - (200GM)","offer_id":46309740642474,"sku":"NOMRP200","price":249.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Moringa_powder_1.webp?v=1762411648"},{"product_id":"organic-wheatgrass-powder-improved-immunity","title":"Organic Wheatgrass Powder for Improved Immunity \u0026 Digestion","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eWheatgrass is considered as a superfood in and is known to be a rich source of antioxidants, vitamins, minerals, and anti-inflammatory properties. It is a type of grass that grows on freshly sprouted wheat seeds. It is a popular dietary supplement, most effective when consumed in the form of any drink. neuherbs Organic Wheatgrass Powder is 10% Natural \u0026amp; pure.  The flavonoids present in Wheatgrass can help flush out toxins from the body, improve immune response, and take care of gut health. It helps manage various common digestive issues like constipation, bloating, gas, and upset stomach. The chlorophyll in wheatgrass is a rich source of magnesium that can naturally regulate bowel movements and improve inflammation. So, improve immunity, detoxify your body, and boost digestion naturally with neuherbs Organic Wheatgrass Powder – a 100% safe, natural, and organic Ayurvedic Product for gut health \u0026amp; overall well-being.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Pack of 1 - (100 GM)","offer_id":43426163392682,"sku":"NOWGP100","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Pack of 2  - (100+100)GM","offer_id":45801918398634,"sku":"NOWGP100P2","price":398.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Wheatgrass_powder_1.webp?v=1760080077"},{"product_id":"organic-triphala-powder-digestive-health-immunity","title":"Triphala Powder: Boost Digestion \u0026 Immunity","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eTriphala is a powerful Ayurvedic Herbal preparation, described as Rasayana, and is used extensively for its antioxidant, anti-inflammatory, and antibacterial benefits. Triphala, meaning three fruits, has myriad health benefits, including promoting digestive health, oral health, immunity \u0026amp; detoxification. The antioxidant, antimicrobial, and anti-inflammatory properties in Triphala are known to fight free radical damage and reduce oxidative stress. This may assist in weight loss and boost metabolism. Which is why we bring to you, neuherbs Organic Triphala Powder which contains natural properties that improve gut health and boost immunity naturally. It has been extensively recommended to help maintain a healthy digestive system managing indigestion, gas, and bloating alongside healthy gut flora.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Pack of 1 - (100 GM)","offer_id":43426199437482,"sku":"NOTPP100","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Pack of 2 - (100+100)GM","offer_id":45801935700138,"sku":"NOTPP100P2","price":398.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Triphala_powder_1.webp?v=1771586773"},{"product_id":"spirulina-tablet","title":"Organically Spirulina Tablets for High Energy, Immunity and Weight Management for Men and Women","description":"\u003cp\u003eSpirulina is one of the most nutritionally dense substances known to man, with antioxidants, phytonutrients, probiotics, along with micro and macronutrients, alongside vitamins such as beta carotene, vitamin C, and vitamin E or minerals such as iron, calcium, chromium, copper, phosphorus, and potassium. Spirulina has several health benefits. We at neuherbs bring to you the goodness of spirulina, in a convenient tablet form, to help you avail its nutritional benefits whenever convenient, throughout the day. Thus, neuherbs Spirulina tablets made with 100% natural \u0026amp; Organic spirulina in tiny tablets compared to regular tablets thus are easy to incorporate into your daily routine and also do not contain any artificial additives which maintains its purity as well as safety. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Smart Pack - (120 Tablets)","offer_id":43954400493738,"sku":"NST120","price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard_1_24027813.jpg?v=1763725053"},{"product_id":"moringa-tablet","title":"Organically Certified Moringa Tablet for High Energy, Detoxification and overall wellness for Men and Women","description":"\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\" class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs bring to you the goodness of Organic Moringa in the form of easy-to-use tablets that are enriched with essential nutrients to help you enjoy every day with full energy. Neuherbs Moringa Tablets are made from pure, natural organic moringa leaf powder without added preservatives, colour or any extra additives, which as per studies are a rich source of protein, vitamins, minerals, fiber \u0026amp; antioxidants. Organic Moringa tablets can be easily incorporated into daily lifestyles to obtain their natural health advantages including high energy, stronger immunity, body detoxification, reduced inflammation \u0026amp; holistic wellness. So, add this magical herb to your diet \u0026amp; avail yourself of several health benefits with it. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Smart Pack - (120 Tablets)","offer_id":43954501943466,"sku":"NMT120","price":299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/moringa_tablets_1.png?v=1754393627"},{"product_id":"true-calcium-plant-based-vitamin-d3","title":"True Calcium Tablets with Plant Vitamin D3 for Stronger Bones","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAn amazing 3-in-1 supplement for daily bone and muscle care, neuherbs True Calcium supplement by neuherbs contains 1000 mg of calcium in a more bioavailable Calcium Citrate form, more-bioavailable Vitamin D3, and natural Magnesium. All three vital nutrients work together to maintain strong bones, increase bone density, support muscle, tendon relaxation and contraction, reducing the risk of fractures and brittle bones later in life. True Calcium, the plant-based calcium tablets, help fill the daily calcium gap in adults. Paired with Vitamin D3 it supports better absorption of calcium in the body. Th unique combination of magnesium \u0026amp; calcium in these calcium tablets for bones works synergistically to support muscles contraction, relaxation \u0026amp; improve overall flexibility.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Monthly Pack - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":44271815033002,"sku":"NTC60","price":299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Saver Pack - (120 Tablets)","offer_id":46152267366570,"sku":"NTC60P2","price":598.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/true_calcium_tablets_1.png?v=1747133307"},{"product_id":"mini-deep-sea-fish-oil-1000-mg","title":"Mini Deep Sea Fish Oil 1000 mg (Lemon Flavour)","description":"\u003cp\u003eAre you looking for fish oil small capsules that are easy to swallow? neuherbs’ Mini Deep Sea Fish Oil Capsules solves your problem. Introducing the most potent source of Omega-3 fatty acids in a remarkably compact form. While regular \u003cstrong\u003efish oil capsules\u003c\/strong\u003e can be large and difficult to swallow, these omega 3 mini capsules offer a convenient and effective alternative.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThese small size \u003cstrong\u003eomega 3 capsules\u003c\/strong\u003e are 50% smaller than regular fish oil capsules, yet they deliver double the strength, providing 360mg of EPA and 240mg of DHA per softgel. Each mini fish oil pill also contains Vitamin E (100% RDA) and Vitamin D3 (100% RDA) to improve bone and skin health.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn addition, forget about the unpleasant fishy taste – these mini fish oil capsules are infused with a refreshing lemon flavour to eliminate fishy aftertaste and burps.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eMini Deep Sea Fish Oil Capsules Benefits\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs the only brand offering smallest fish oil capsules in India in natural lemon flavour, neuherbs scientifically researched product delivers a range of health benefits:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImproves Heart Health: Omega-3 fatty acids, especially EPA, help maintain healthy cholesterol levels and blood pressure.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnhances Brain Function: DHA are crucial for cognitive function, memory, and focus.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReduces Inflammation: Omega-3s possess anti-inflammatory properties that may help alleviate joint pain and muscle soreness.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eVitamins D and E: Vitamin E improves absorption of Omega-3s, while Vitamin D ensures healthy bones and cartilage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eneuherbs Quality Assurance\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs is committed to delivering the highest quality omega 3 fish oil mini softgels in India. We test the fish for heavy metal toxicity, including mercury, cobalt, copper, and cadmium, through a process called molecular distillation that offers 100% accurate results. In addition, each batch undergoes rigorous ten-step testing for purity, potency, and freshness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eRecommended Dosage and Packaging\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs \u003cstrong\u003eomega 3 fish oil\u003c\/strong\u003e mini softgels are available in packs of 120 capsules. For best results, take one small fish oil pill twice daily with a meal.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eConsult an expert for free to learn more about your heart health and the benefits of Omega-3 fish oils. Add neuherbs’ Mini Deep Sea Fish Oil Capsules to your everyday routine and experience the numerous benefits of concentrated Omega-3s.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Mini Fish Oil - (120 Softgel)","offer_id":44930057732266,"sku":"NMDSFO120","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Mini Fish Oil - (60 Softgel)","offer_id":47466409525418,"sku":"NMDSFO60","price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Mini Fish Oil - (200 Softgel)","offer_id":44930057765034,"sku":"NMDSFO200","price":999.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Mini_deep_sea_fish_oil_120.webp?v=1772186300"},{"product_id":"omega-flaxseed-oil","title":"Flaxseed Oil Capsules 1000mg With 821mg Omega 3-6-9, Additional Vitamin D3 \u0026 E To Support Heart, Joint \u0026 Skin For Women \u0026 Men","description":"\u003cp\u003eAre you a vegetarian? Wondering how to incorporate\u003cstrong\u003e Omege-3s\u003c\/strong\u003e into your daily diet? neuherbs has made it easy for you. Introducing neuherbs’ Flaxseed Oil Capsules 1000mg - your plant-based Omega-3-6-9 powerhouse.  The supplement is a natural and potent source of Omega-3 fatty acids derived from flaxseeds. While fish oil is a popular choice, flaxseed oil provides a vegetarian and vegan-friendly option, rich in alpha-linolenic acid (ALA), a precursor to EPA and DHA.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs flaxseed oil capsules deliver a 500mg concentrated dose of ALA, supporting overall health and well-being. It also contains 134 mg of Omega-6 (Linoleic acid) and 187mg of Omega-9 (Oleic acid).\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn addition, the \u003cstrong\u003eOmega-3 flaxseed oil supplements\u003c\/strong\u003e are fortified with Vitamin D and Vitamin E to enhance bone and skin health.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eFlaxseed Oil Capsules 1000mg Benefits\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs one of the best flaxseed oil capsules in India, neuherbs scientifically-researched product offers a range of health benefits:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSupports Heart Health: Flaxseed Omega-3 fatty acids contribute to cardiovascular wellness by helping maintain healthy cholesterol levels and blood pressure.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePromotes Brain Function: ALA is converted into EPA and DHA, which are crucial for cognitive function, memory, and focus.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReduces Inflammation: Omega-3s possess anti-inflammatory properties that may help alleviate joint pain, muscle soreness, and other inflammatory conditions.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProtects Bone Health: neuherbs flaxseed oil capsules contain plant-based Vitamin D3, which supports bone health and improves signs of deficiency, such as back pain and buckling joints.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSupports Healthy Skin and Hair: ALA contributes to skin hydration and elasticity, promoting a healthy complexion and lustrous hair. The addition of Vitamin E, which is a potent antioxidant, further intensifies the results.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFlaxseed oil benefits for females: Omega-3 fatty acids, DHA in particular, help in foetal brain development, improving cognitive power and eye health in the womb. Vegetarian moms can also consume neuherbs Omega 3 flaxseed oil tablets to reduce the risks of preterm delivery.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eneuherbs Quality Assurance\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs is committed to delivering the highest quality \u003cstrong\u003eomega-3 flaxseed oil capsules\u003c\/strong\u003e in India. Our flaxseeds are carefully selected from top organic farmers and cold-pressed to preserve their natural goodness. Each batch undergoes ten-step rigorous testing for purity, potency, and freshness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFurthermore, the capsules do not contain additives, artificial colours, trans fats, or preservatives.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eRecommended Dosage and Packaging\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs omega 3 flaxseed oil tablets are available in packs of 60 capsules. For best results, take one softgel twice daily with a meal for at least three months. Since it is a natural product, it is recommended to store it in a cool, dry, and dark place to avoid rancidification.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTo know more about your heart health and the benefits of Omgea-3 flaxseed oils, consult an expert for free.  Add neuherbs Flaxseed Oil Capsules 1000mg to your everyday meals and experience the numerous benefits of plant-based omega-3s.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Smart Pack - 60 Capsules","offer_id":44650834428074,"sku":"NOFSO60","price":499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Value Pack - 120 Capsules","offer_id":46122553442474,"sku":"NOFSO60P2","price":998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Flaxseed_oil_capsule_1.webp?v=1772175772"},{"product_id":"mens-wellness-combo-true-vitamin-pure-shilajit","title":"Men's Wellness Combo: True Vitamin \u0026 Pure Himalayan Shilajit","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eneuherbs True Vitamin and Pure Himalayan Men's Wellness Combo offers a comprehensive solution for men seeking to optimize their health and well-being. True Vitamin provides a potent blend of essential vitamins and minerals, supporting overall vitality and energy levels. Combined with the Pure Himalayan Shilajit for men, this combo delivers targeted nutrients that address specific health concerns commonly faced by men, such as prostate health, testosterone levels, and stress management. By nourishing your body with essential nutrients and addressing unique male health needs, this combo empowers you to live a healthier, more fulfilling life. \u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (30Tabs + 20GM)","offer_id":44715475173546,"sku":"NMSWC2","price":998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/20g_tv_30n_FRONT__1.jpg?v=1729160346"},{"product_id":"true-multivitamin-tablets-women-health","title":"True Vitamin Women: Multivitamin Tablets For Women","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated explicitly for adult women to help manage their daily nutritional needs. neuherbs True Vitamin Women multivitamin tablets contains 34 ingredients including four essential blends that provide comprehensive wellness support. The multivitamin tablets offer 100% RDA of essential vitamins with vital minerals, amino acids, and plant-based vitamin D3, which help women nourish and improve their bones, heart, immunity, and hair- skin effectively. These multivitamin tablets for women help manage hormonal balance, elevated mood and poor reproductive health. The amino acids with vitamin b complex help with fatigue and boost energy levels required to carry out daily tasks effectively.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (30 Tablets)","offer_id":44862088511658,"sku":"NTVW30","price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"2 Month Pack (Recommended) - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":46122548265130,"sku":"NTVW30P2","price":698.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/True_Multivitamin_women_1.jpg?v=1742446747"},{"product_id":"true-multivitamin-adult-40-plus-tablets","title":"True Multivitamin Adult 40+ Tablets - Immunity, Energy, Digestion","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eScientifically designed for men and women above 40 years of age, neuherbs True Multivitamin Adults 40+ tablet is made with 13 vitamins, 9 minerals and unique herbal blend essential for the body’s optimal functioning that naturally starts declining after 40. True multivitamin tablets offer great digestive benefits due to the presence of digestive enzymes \u0026amp;amp; probiotics content in it, helping you in smooth digestion, better nutrient absorption and happy mood as well. A natural blend of ginseng and L lysine may improve metabolism and overall energy levels considerably. Its herbal blend containing ayurvedic herbs like Brahmi and Bhringraj helps calm the mind, improve focus \u0026amp;amp; mental clarity. neuherbs True Multivitamin Adults 40+ is further enriched with plant-based Vitamin D3 to maintain healthy bones \u0026amp;amp; maximize well-being.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Starter Pack - (45 Tablets)","offer_id":44862118133930,"sku":"NTVA40P45","price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Saver Pack- (90 Tablets)","offer_id":46152294531242,"sku":"NTVA40P45P2","price":898.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/True_multivitamin_adult_1.jpg?v=1742471918"},{"product_id":"gokshura-tablet","title":"Ayurvedic Gokshura Tablet For Men Wellness - Improves Vitality \u0026 strength, Helps Boost Testosterone Levels","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGokushura or Tribulus terrestris contains the active ingredient saponins and has long been used in Ayurveda as a tonic or rasayana for its antioxidant and anti-inflammatory properties and is known to help maintain hormonal balance in the body. Studies show that Gokshura or Gokshura tablets are used to increase testosterone levels in the body, which can improve strength, endurance, men's personal health, muscle recovery, growth, and overall vitality. neuherbs brings to you its Gokshura Tablets which contain the goodness of high strength gokshura – yielding a 1000 mg intake per serving. neuherbs Gokshura tablets also contain extra support of kali mirch which contains 95% piperine that is known to improve absorption and provide better wellness results to you. When consumed regularly, the natural herbal powder can enhance stamina and endurance, which is beneficial for athletes, bodybuilders, and people who want to gain muscle mass.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Monthly Pack - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":44911572844714,"sku":"NGT60","price":275.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Saver Pack - (120 Tablets)","offer_id":46152279490730,"sku":"NGT60P2","price":550.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Gokshura_tablets_1.jpg?v=1744634212"},{"product_id":"shilajit-gold-ultra-capsules-men-stamina","title":"Shilajit Gold Ultra Capsules to Boost Men's Performance","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eneuherbs Shilajit Ultra Gold Capsule for men, has 11 powerful Ayurvedic ingredients such as \u0026amp;\u0026amp; Ashwagandha, Shatavari, Cinnamon, Gokshura, Lavang, Jaiphal, kesar, and Swarna Bhasma. Ayurveda says these ingredients are used as Rasayana, to promote longevity, energy levels and stamina. The herbs have antioxidant, anti-inflammatory, rejuvenating properties, helping with endurance, stamina, performance and motivation. Shilajit gold ultra capsules also help in enhancing mood, sleep and reduce stress offering a positive effect on overall testosterone levels. The addition of kali mirch extract also known as piperine ensures that the body absorbs the nutrients present in neuherbs Shilajit Ultra Gold Capsules effectively, making our shilajit capsules one of the most effective in increasing your performance \u0026amp; stamina!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Smart Pack - 60 Capsules","offer_id":44919565713578,"sku":"NSGU60","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Value Pack - 120 Capsules","offer_id":46122557571242,"sku":"NSGU60P2","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Shilajit_gold_ultra_capsules_1.png?v=1751715137"},{"product_id":"true-magnesium-tablets-relax-muscles-mind","title":"True Magnesium Tablets - Relax Muscles \u0026 Mind, Support Bones","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMagnesium is essential for proper heart function, energy production, hormonal balance, and muscle function. It is essentially known as the “Miracle Mineral” because of its versatile benefits. It also helps our body absorb Vitamin D3 better, promotes healthy nervous function, improves bone health, calms the mind, regulates insulin production, and keeps the body energized throughout the day. neuherbs True Magnesium is a high strength formula that contains 1600 mg of magnesium, that is uniquely paired with Zinc, Vitamin C, antioxidants like Blueberry, and Bilberry for maximum benefits. True Magnesium is created to fulfil your body’s daily magnesium needs. True Magnesium supplement contains 353mg of elemental Magnesium Bisglycinate in a more bioavailable form which is gentle on stomach. It effectively contributes to keeping the muscle relaxed, helps improve energy levels, promote sound sleep, calms the mind, fights free-radical damage, improves immunity \u0026amp; promote better muscle recovery.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Value Pack - (120 Tablets)","offer_id":48022649733290,"sku":"NTMG120","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Smart Pack - 60 Tablets","offer_id":44923837153450,"sku":"NTMG60","price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/True_magnesium_tablets_9.webp?v=1771494334"},{"product_id":"b12-vitamin-tablets-energy-circulation","title":"Plant-Based True Vitamin B12 Tablets For Energy \u0026 Brain","description":"\u003cp\u003eVitamin B12 deficiency can lead to tiredness, muscle soreness, muscle cramps, uninvited fatigue, depression, and even mood swings. Vitamin B12 supplements are best for vegans \u0026amp; vegetarians that may promote better circulation, improve concentration and memory, keep the mind calm, promote nerve health, reduce tiredness, improve energy levels, and boost metabolic processes. It's the best Vitamin B12 supplement which consists of natural Vitamin B12 derived from spirulina to help you fulfill your daily Vitamin B12 needs. True B12 Vitamin tablet for men and women with Myo-Inositol which help promote better absorption that help maintain optimal brain functioning, reduce stress \u0026amp; anxiety and is a good mood enhancer. In addition, neuherbs True B12 Vitamin also contains folic acid and the goodness of Punarnava. Punarnava is best known for its rejuvenating properties that help the body recover oxidative stress and rejuvenate the body from within.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Monthly Pack - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":44928074416298,"sku":"NTB1260","price":275.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Saver Pack - (120 Tablets)","offer_id":46152288469162,"sku":"NTB1260P2","price":549.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/true_b12_tablets_1.png?v=1744629336"},{"product_id":"skin-glow-collagen-powder-glowing-skin","title":"Skin Glow Collagen Powder for Glowing Skin","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSkin collagen is the most found protein in our body that is known to manage skin texture, skin elasticity, and skin health. If you wish to have young and wrinkle-free skin forever, you must source collagen externally from the best collagen supplements and consume it regularly. neuherbs offers the best collagen supplement for the skin with dual action formula- it does not offer collagen to skin but also boost up natural collagen production in the body. neuherbs Collagen booster powder is loaded with hyaluronic acid and biotin. neuherbs Skin Glow Collagen is made from type 1 hydrolyzed marine collagen peptide and glucosamine, which can help renewing the lost collagen \u0026amp; support reducing early signs of ageing with better absorption \u0026amp; efficacy thus bringing back skin's elasticity \u0026amp; firmness. Skin Glow Collagen supplement can further help in boosting collagen with the help of hyaluronic acid, vitamin C, E \u0026amp; Biotin with no artificial preservatives \u0026amp; colours. Enjoy skin glow collagen in two fun flavours- Orange \u0026amp; Litchi.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Orange Flavour - 200gm","offer_id":44941106217130,"sku":"NSGC200OF","price":799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Litchi Flavour - 200gm","offer_id":44941107495082,"sku":"NSGC200LF","price":799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/marinecollagenboosterinindia.webp?v=1766145173"},{"product_id":"true-vitamin-wellness-combo-women-adults","title":"True Vitamin Wellness Combo for Women \u0026 Adults 40+","description":"\u003cp\u003eNutritional needs are bound to change for individuals at different stages of their lives. A man will have different needs from a woman, a 20 year old will have different nutritional needs from a 40 year old. While some nutritions are consistently required in humans, multivitamins need to cater to the specific needs of people. To target this very need, neuherbs bring to you our True Multivitamin Adults 40+ and True vitamin Women combo —- to help you address daily nutritional gaps at different stages of life. True Vitamin Women multivitamin tablets for women help with reproductive health, their hair, skin or bone health and helps them maintain high energy levels throughout their day. On the other hand, multivitamins for adults above 40 are formulated using natural herbs \u0026amp; other ingredients rich in vitamins, minerals, along with probiotics \u0026amp; digestive enzymes to support bone health, digestion and energy metabolism within the body. Both of these supplement show our wide variety of products and dedication in bringing wellness to you, while also proving to be a valuable addition to your daily balanced diets.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Wellness Pack - (30N + 45N)","offer_id":45047688626346,"sku":"NTVWA40C2","price":798.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/True_multivitamin_Combo_for_Women_and_Adults_1.png?v=1744023011"},{"product_id":"pure-himalayan-shilajit-gummies-stamina","title":"Pure Himalayan Shilajit Gummies 30 (Tamarind Flavour) for Stamina","description":"\u003cp\u003eShilajit is a traditional Ayurvedic herb that has been used for centuries to treat people with low stamina, endurance, and vitality. neuherbs Pure Himalayan Shilajit Gummies are not only powerfully packed with original Himalayan shilajit resin, sourced from the high altitudes of the Himalayas, but are also available in a delicious and effortless gummy format. This new Shilajit resin gummy is recognized as the best gummies for strength, stamina and vitality, and uniquely delivers the benefits of Shilajit; with the added deliciousness of tamarind flavour! Offering all the advantages of pure shilajit resin, neuherbs Shilajit gummies provide a convenient option that can be consumed without water, offering flexibility and ease of consumption. Whether you need an energy boost before a workout or desire a sweet indulgence after a meal, simply chew these gummies anytime, anywhere, for an effortless wellness experience. The shilajit gummies are free from added sugar, artificial preservatives \u0026amp; gelatin free.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Smart Pack- 30N Gummies","offer_id":45124596891818,"sku":"NPHSG30TMF","p