ption":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs Deep-Sea Fish Oil Capsules value pack with Shilajit Resin offer a powerful combination of scientifically tested nature-driven ingredients for enhanced wellness. Fish oil provides essential omega-3 fatty acids, known for their anti-inflammatory properties and support for heart, brain, bone \u0026amp; muscles health. Shilajit, a fulvic acid-rich mineral, is believed to possess adaptogenic properties, helping the body adapt to stress and promote strength, stamina \u0026amp; vitality while offering antioxidants to the body for repair \u0026amp; recovery. Together, these ingredients create a synergistic blend that supports heart health, cognitive function, and energy levels. \u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Fish Oil Capsules - (200 Softgel)","offer_id":46108222226602,"sku":"NPPC2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/omega3fishoil.jpg?v=1719481345"},{"product_id":"fish-oil-capsules-with-multivitamin-tablets","title":"Deep Sea Fish Oil Capsules With Free True Vitamin Tablets","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs Deep-Sea Fish Oil Capsules and True Vitamin Multivitamin Tablets offer a powerful combination to support your overall health and fitness regimen. The fish oil capsules provide essential omega-3 fatty acids, known for their anti-inflammatory properties and benefits for heart health, brain function, and skin health. Omega-3 helps fitness overs by reducing muscle inflammation, promoting muscle strength. Combined with the True Vitamin multivitamin tablets, this combo delivers a comprehensive blend of vitamins and minerals to ensure optimal nutrient intake and support various bodily functions such as keeping you energetic all day long with high strength \u0026amp; immunity. Together, these supplements work in harmony to promote a healthier, more balanced lifestyle for you.  \u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Fish oil - (200 Softgel)","offer_id":46109820813482,"sku":"NSBVPC2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/200n_30n__1.jpg?v=1729163069"},{"product_id":"pure-himalayan-shilajit-resin-15g","title":"Pure Himalayan Shilajit Resin 15g - Stamina Booster","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 12.0pt 0in 12.0pt 0in;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\"\u003eShilajit is a traditional Ayurvedic herb that has been used for centuries to enhance stamina and vitality of the individuals consuming it. neuherbs Shilajit Resin is made with Pure Himalayan Shilajit sourced from the highest altitudes to ensure the most natural, best quality Shilajit Resin online for you. Shilajit is widely celebrated for its benefit to one’s skin health, mind, energy, mood or vitality. Providing all the advantages of the beneficial Shilajit, neuherbs Shilajit resin help mediate the benefits of this Ayurvedic herb from the peaks of Himalayan mountains to your wellbeing, offering a convenient option that can be consumed anytime around the day. So whether it is some energy boost that you need before workout or anytime of the day.neuherbs Shilajit Resin provides several benefits to your well-being —- helping you feel different in your daily lifestyle. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Shilajit - (15gm)","offer_id":46144601882794,"sku":"NPHS15","price":499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/shialjitresinwithspoon.jpg?v=1721287330"},{"product_id":"deep-sea-cod-liver-oil-capsules-for-heart-brain","title":"Deep Sea Cod Liver Oil Capsules for Heart \u0026 Brain","description":"\u003cp\u003eAre you looking for a natural alternative to fish oil supplements to boost your heart and brain health? \u003cstrong\u003eCod liver oil capsules\u003c\/strong\u003e are an excellent choice. neuherbs Deep Sea Cod Liver Oil Capsules 600 mg offer a potent blend of Omega-3 fatty acids (180mg), Vitamin D3, and Vitamin E in one convenient soft gel. Obtained from the depths of the Atlantic and Pacific oceans, our cod liver oil is a rich source of essential nutrients that support overall well-being.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCod fish is a time-tested source of Omega-3s, known for their numerous health benefits. These fish get their Omega-3s by absorbing the microalgae after consuming phytoplanktons. Each capsule contains high levels of EPA and DHA, vital for maintaining a healthy heart and sharp mind. Cod liver oil also contains vitamins A and D and remarkable anti-inflammatory properties. So, with neuherbs, you not only get the benefits of Omega-3 fatty acids, but also 100% RDA of Vitamin A, D, and E.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhat’s more? Our lemon-flavoured capsules eliminate the unpleasant aftertaste and fishy burps commonly associated with cod liver oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eCod Liver Oil Capsules Benefits\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs Deep Sea Cod Liver Oil Capsules offer a range of health benefits:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eKeeps Your Heart Healthy: Omega-3 fatty acids help maintain healthy cholesterol levels and blood pressure, promoting cardiovascular wellness.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImproves Your Brain Function: DHA is crucial for cognitive function, memory, and focus, supporting a sharp and healthy mind.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBoosts Your Immunity: Vitamin D3 and anti-inflammatory drugs help modulate the immune system and keep infections at bay.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMaintains Healthy Bones: Vitamin D3 is essential for calcium absorption and bone health, ensuring you have stronger bones, cartilage, and muscles.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOffers Antioxidant Support: Vitamin E acts as a powerful antioxidant, protecting cells from oxidative damage. This helps improve gut, skin, and hair health.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNourishes Skin: The anti-inflammatory properties and antioxidants together help boost skin cell production, protect them from stress and inflammation, and reduce the signs of ageing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eCod Liver Oil Benefits for Female\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOmega-3 fatty acids, particularly DHA, are essential during pregnancy for fetal brain development. It can potentially improve your unborn baby’s brain function and retina development. By taking the best cod liver oil for adults, you can also reduce the risks of preterm delivery.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eneuherbs Quality Check\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs delivers high-quality health supplements with scientifically tested formulations. Our Deep Sea Cod Liver Oil undergoes molecular distillation and third-party testing for purity, efficiency, and safety. Free from preservatives, artificial colours, flavours, and gluten, they are the best cod liver oil capsules in India.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eDosage and Packaging\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs \u003cstrong\u003eDeep Sea Cod Liver Oil Capsules Omega 3\u003c\/strong\u003e are available in bottles of 100 capsules. For best results, take one capsule twice daily with a meal.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eConsult with a healthcare professional to learn more about your specific health needs and the benefits of Omega-3 fatty acids, Vitamin D3, and Vitamin E.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Deep Sea Cod Liver - (100 softgel)","offer_id":46151832600746,"sku":"NDSCLO100","price":299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Deep_sea_cod_liver_oil_1.webp?v=1767179761"},{"product_id":"true-vitamin-women-30-tablets-skin-collagen-booster-210-g-combo","title":"True Vitamin Women 30 Tablets \u0026 Skin Collagen Booster 210 g Combo","description":"\u003cp\u003eIndulge in your wellness with our True Vitamin Women and Collagen Booster Combo. This comprehensive package combines the power of our True Vitamin Multivitamin Tablets for women and Skin Collagen Booster 210g, providing essential nutrients and support for your overall health and beauty. Our Multivitamin Tablets offer a carefully balanced blend of vitamins and minerals to nourish your body, boost energy levels, and strengthen your reproductive system. Meanwhile, our Skin Collagen Booster is packed with plant-based collagen boosters to promote healthy skin, hair, and nails. With regular use, you can experience improved skin elasticity, reduced wrinkles, and enhanced youthfulness. Our products are made with high-quality ingredients and are free from artificial additives, ensuring optimal results. So, invest in your well-being and discover the transformative power with our True Vitamin Combo — helping you glow both inside and out.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Monthly Pack- (30 tablets + 200g)","offer_id":46254897365162,"sku":"NSWC2","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\