n, specifically designed for people above the age of 40. neuherbs True Multivitamin Adults 40+ tablets are created with 13 vitamins, 9 minerals, and one of its kind herbal blends serving various purposes for our body’s optimal functioning. Particularly catering to the heart, immunity, and bones the combo also brings to you the goodness of neuherbs Deep Sea Omega Fish Oil soft gels that contain triple strength Omega- 3 Fatty Acid, procured from the best quality deep sea fish oil to better manage your heart health, muscle function, memory \u0026amp; bone health. Available in lemon flavour, it is a one of its kind Omega supplement as this helps with fishy aftertaste or helps avoid fishy burps after taking the supplement. So, buy Deep Sea Omega Fish Oil soft gels alongside True Multivitamin for Adults 40+ in the unique combination brought to you by neuherbs and provide your body with the antioxidants that it needs and manage your bone and joint health effectively. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Monthly Pack - (60 Softgels+ 45 Tablets)","offer_id":46254929969322,"sku":"NAWC2","price":1148.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/FISHOIL_MULTIVITAMINADULTS_1_1.jpg?v=1734593201"},{"product_id":"true-vitamin-60-tablets-true-vitamin-women-30-tablets-true-vitamin-adults-40-45-tablets-combo","title":"True Vitamin 60 Tablets \u0026 True Vitamin Women 30 Tablets \u0026 True Vitamin Adults 40+ 45 Tablets Combo","description":"\u003cp\u003eBuy neuherbs True Vitamin, True Vitamin for Women and True Multivitamin Adults 40+ combo and ensure overall well-being of all people around you. Be it the men, women or their grandparents, neuherbs True Vitamin range are meant for people across all ages and walks of life and seeks to bring a healthier lifestyle in your household. neuherbs True Vitamin Multivitamin tablets are power-packed with Vitamins A, E, C, D, and B complex, while also bringing to you a blend of minerals like Zinc or copper along with several essential antioxidants. Meanwhile, neuherbs True Vitamin Women is one of the best multivitamins for women, created explicitly for adult women to help manage their skin, hair, immunity, energy, bones \u0026amp; hormones. It contains 34 ingredients and four essential blends that provide comprehensive wellness support and fulfils your daily nutritional needs. Lastly, neuherbs True Multivitamin Adults 40+ multivitamin tablets are created with 13 vitamins, 9 minerals, and a unique herbal blend that is vital for our body’s optimal functioning. It particularly manages low energy levels, digestions, immunity, and bones. The super potent energy blend of natural ginseng and L-lysine helps improve metabolism and overall energy levels. It has also proven to be greatly important for an individual’s heart health —- a rising concern for people aged 40+ in India.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Family Pack- (60 + 30 + 45 Tablets)","offer_id":46258899910826,"sku":"NTFWC3","price":1189.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/true_multivitamin_men_women_tablet_1.png?v=1744008049"},{"product_id":"shilajit-gold-ultra-resin-20g","title":"Shilajit Gold Ultra Resin 20g - Powerful Stamina Booster","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-teams=\"true\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"ui-provider a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003eExperience the transformative benefits of our 100% Pure Shilajit Gold Resin, rich in 75% fulvic acid, meticulously sourced from the pristine heights of the Himalayas at 18,000 ft. blended with ayurvedic herbs to increase the efficiency. This high potency formula combines Shilajit with 6 Ayurvedic herbs such as Safed Musli, Ashwagandha, Gokshura, Saffron, Trikatu \u0026amp; Swarna Bhasma ensuring maximum potency and unparalleled benefits. Rich in Fulvic Acid and withanolides, this natural performance booster may help reduce inflammation, enhances strength, stamina, and overall athletic performance while promoting faster muscle recovery. Enhanced with Trikatu and Swarna Bhasma, our shilajit ultra resin offers superior bioavailability, and boosts results. neuherbs Shilajit Gold Ultra Resin is rigorously tested for heavy metals, making it the ideal addition to your fitness regimen for natural vitality and performance enhancement. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Shilajit Gold Resin- (20 g)","offer_id":46286261059754,"sku":"NSGUR20","price":999.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard13copy_c9a37aba-639d-49a9-afc1-d48213c946f7.jpg?v=1728457978"}],"url":"https:\/\/neuherbs.com\/collections\/premium-health-products.oembed?page=4","provider":"Neuherbs","version":"1.0","type":"link"}